headline: Argus Raises Atmos Energy (ATO) PT to $165 on Strong Fundamentals
summary: On Wednesday, Argus raised its price target for Atmos Energy Corporation (NYSE:ATO) to $165 from $155, while maintaining a Buy rating. This adjustment reflects the company’s solid fundamentals and the stock’s appeal within the Utilities sector during a period of declining interest rates. Atmos Energy reported a diluted EPS of $3.03 for the FQ2 2025, […]
